  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Viscum Album Mother Tincture as an Anti-hypertensive in Essential Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Viscum Album Mother Tincture as an Anti-hypertensive in Essential Hypertension. One Group Pretest Posttest Design</official_title>
