  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To estimate the effectiveness of Viscum album Homoeopathic mother tincture in Essential
      Hypertension by conducting clinical trial in moderate hypertensive patients for a period of
      six weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
