    <measure>change in Serum CKMB</measure>
    <time_frame>12 weeks and 16 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>The blood sample was collected at the end of 12 weeks of medication followed by a drug free period of 4 weeks.The blood sample was collected again at the end of 4 weeks of drug free period to ascertain serum CKMB.</description>
